First, run:
g++ -Wall -g -std=c++11 -I /usr/local/Cellar/xerces-c/3.2.3/include/ -L /usr/local/Cellar/xerces-c/3.2.3/lib/ ./*cpp -o XMLExample -lxerces-c -lcurses

Second, choose one of the below to run
./XMLExample wear.xml
./XMLExample badScroll.xml
./XMLExample dropPack.xml
./XMLExample death.xml
./XMLExample dungeon.xml
./XMLExample hallucinate.xml
./XMLExample testDrawing.xml
./XMLExample testPassage.xml
